content:
First case of coronavirus confirmed in Belgium. The authorities of Belgium today confirmed the first case in the country of the new Coronavirus (2019-NCOV) in a person who was repatriated from the Chinese city of Wuhan, a focus of an outbreak of the disease, which already killed 426 people. The Belgian Ministry of Health has released today that the person has good health and does not show any symptoms of the disease.

This person was among nine Belgians repatriated from Wuhan, China, which occurred this weekend. The infected patient was taken to a special hospital for more care, while the other repatriates remain under observation.




